== D.4 — The Cotton Wick Test

The non-negotiable quality check for the menstruum before any extraction is begun.

#lab[
  *Protocol:*
  + Dip a cotton wick (or twisted cotton thread) into the spirit.
  + Remove and allow excess to drip off for two seconds.
  + Bring a flame to the wick.
  + *Pass:* The flame holds on the wick itself and burns it cleanly.
  + *Fail:* The flame extinguishes when it reaches the wick, or the wick does not ignite.

  A failing spirit must be rectified further by additional distillation before use. Do not proceed with a failing spirit under any circumstances.
]